pageTitle: Police moving next door to City Hall | LaRueCountyHerald.com
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {27532=The LaRue County Herald News | circulation@laruecountyherald.com | 270-358-3118 40 Shawnee Drive, Hodgenville, KY 42748 Office Hours are 8:00 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. Monday through Friday, 34724=Copyright © 2015, 21708=Hodgenville City Police will move to the former First Baptist Church educational building next to city hall by the first of the year.
